data.description: MOVE IN READY large and spacious home on a premium PRIVATE preserve lot with a fully FENCED in yard and SCREENED porch. This home built by Richmond American has several upgrades including GRANITE counter space throughout. Additional features include 42'' cabinets, OPEN style gourmet kitchen with GRANITE island, walk-in closets, 2-car garage, laundry room and all ONE LEVEL living with plenty of STORAGE. This Woodbridge community is 15 minutes from the beaches and Amelia island. This home is also centrally located to major highways, military bases and the Jacksonville International Airport. Come enjoy the FERNANDINA BEACH community and book a tour TODAY so you don't miss out!
